ng to\n\nOPERATIVE PROVISIONS\n\n1 DEFINITIONS\n\n1.1  \u201c Recipient \u201d means the party receiving Confidential Information.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 401, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "70ba83c1-3844-475a-b3e9-33248b3d85a4": {"__data__": {"id_": "70ba83c1-3844-475a-b3e9-33248b3d85a4", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "555aa84f-b95d-4f7c-84ac-a6f64e9221a4", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "91a2a800301b684a106fcf8cda28e4ad622142721f9347f81d1cc1a65f94c550", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "e8de0485-d7b7-408b-9be2-6d6562d9f265", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "cfcc9f2336a7dcadcc143d753f23665e2ded642cbcce5553be169a66b805e695", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "e1682bd2-468c-4ff4-8541-e5ae45b760f8", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "1c7110755e1b0fcbb94c05885ed129e326a59644b9858cdbe120790f261565e7", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "1.2  \u201c Discloser \u201d means the party disclosing Confidential Information to the other party.\n\n1.3  \u201c Purpose \u201d means\n\na)  any discussions and negotiations between or within the parties with respect to or in connection with the establishment of a business relationship between the parties;\n\n and subsequently,\n\nb)  any activities in connection with the business relationship between the parties.\n\n1.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 403, "end_char_idx": 799, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "e1682bd2-468c-4ff4-8541-e5ae45b760f8": {"__data__": {"id_": "e1682bd2-468c-4ff4-8541-e5ae45b760f8", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_me