is agreement by Recipient;\n\nb)  to have had rightfully in its possession prior to disclosure to Recipient by Discloser;\n\nc)  is independently developed by Recipient without the use of any Confidential Information; or\n\nd)  Recipient rightfully obtains from a third party who has the right to transfer or disclose it;", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1750, "end_char_idx": 2146, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "415866c8-33e6-42cc-9200-4e14d99af2e3": {"__data__": {"id_": "415866c8-33e6-42cc-9200-4e14d99af2e3", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "555aa84f-b95d-4f7c-84ac-a6f64e9221a4", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "91a2a800301b684a106fcf8cda28e4ad622142721f9347f81d1cc1a65f94c550", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "368dfc8a-837d-49a0-a0bb-42d7c38f9b3c", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "17343ecd4a4fc81ba61b68c545a2ed8174253ea4b71d69a284919b3fd4b42b7f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "eae28dfc-6f1b-497b-b20a-7dae40ea67bf", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "0c1c747c6bb9820cf54c8d37fe3669289c7d6f93cd797e4707e163a0e5d74669", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "or\n\ne)  was disclosed to a third party with the Discloser's prior written consent; or\n\nwww.anton-paar.com\nSeite 1 von 4\nCONFIDENTIALITY AGREEMENT\n\nf) was disclosed to a third party after the period of seven (7)  years from the date of the disclosure.\n\n2 NON-DISCLOSURE AND NON-USE OF CONFIDENTIAL INFORMATION\n\n2.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2149, "end_char_idx": 2461, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "eae28dfc-6f1b-497b-b20a-7dae40ea67bf": {"__data__": {"id_"